{"tid":2061613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"吳重儀判異見者去精神病院同中共摧毀潑墨女孩一案係同一手法","createTime":"2020-06-12T13:29:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T12:26:56.000Z","uid":26770,"like":114,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"587a3136f37d0a5c1b150564d5ed4647da13402c","tid":2061613,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T13:29:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2046892\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rti.org.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2Fid%2F2046892&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjNjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=5d49768d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2046892</a><br />\n「潑墨女孩」董瑤瓊出院 前後判若兩人<br />\n因向習近平畫像潑墨而在一年半前，被送入精神病院的湖南女子董瑤瓊近日出院回家。據父親董建彪透露，<ins>董瑤瓊已完全判若兩人，甚至出現癡呆症狀。</ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">明顯曾經遭到投毒</span>"},{"pid":"ed13afe6bc4513ee1f3c13926e01ccc3b8ad507e","tid":2061613,"uid":26770,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T13:31:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.rti.org.tw/assets/thumbnails/2020/01/03/27e431613e6925b1f64c454810abbd5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.rti.org.tw%2Fassets%2Fthumbnails%2F2020%2F01%2F03%2F27e431613e6925b1f64c454810abbd5a.jpg&h=395c36c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n右邊係未遭投藥前<br />\n左邊係遭投毒後<br />\n<br />\n基本上已無康復可能<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">而吳重儀判異見者去的小欖係由懲教控制<br />\n香港懲教曾折磨未成年政治犯至嘗試自殺</span>"},{"pid":"0526e2dff731033c44cefad81ed13217a3d7b88c","tid":2061613,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T13:33:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"89b5f0f44d615b12baed84d9efc5cff6bc283ee4","tid":2061613,"uid":148778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T13:33:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f590b8f178bd0f4cf799e4ac9dd4ce99ef5ac419","tid":2061613,"uid":70487,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T13:34:35.000Z","msg":"&quot;&quot;&quot;愛國教育&quot;&quot;&quot;"},{"pid":"c25ed78aea7f42cca24cab7a0cc37f121ef40ea7","tid":2061613,"uid":161821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T13:35:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbe6820a3369c8db964c33f82f34febcdc75c2f8","tid":2061613,"uid":26770,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T13:36:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2005171/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2005171/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n懲教一哥胡英明係2019年2月頭已部署好酷刑迫害政治犯<br />\n引入監控手環防政治犯自殺"},{"pid":"4a1c1487be0802bd04e59b0ef598830ddd28c705","tid":2061613,"uid":47268,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T13:36:34.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b45e3e76fbf2df1ab5077ad636e3d63a5074ac79","tid":2061613,"uid":87891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T13:37:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6486373d892d33b597432105189938b05c7d739d","tid":2061613,"uid":46161,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T13:37:17.000Z","msg":"吳重儀鳩判冇代價"},{"pid":"ae7412a98aaa09e522720f7a1ffc9f431d265eec","tid":2061613,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T13:37:31.000Z","msg":"好嬲"},{"pid":"2d6dd97d05fdd0dca8af5495add4d1eeccab42ea","tid":2061613,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T13:43:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"67d71b318f1b742f7769c4ef50634f804f585b93","tid":2061613,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T13:43:57.000Z","msg":"洗腦手段"},{"pid":"e897954583fb655addb73b2ec37421dda33c5b6c","tid":2061613,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T13:45:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ee23c1e60c31346041fb1965ca6257c2176f41e","tid":2061613,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T13:46:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f249e2feb53053570366bd5fc86c2d8a474f9ca9","tid":2061613,"uid":35364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T13:47:00.000Z","msg":"<strong>蘇聯精神病學的政治濫用</strong><br />\n在蘇聯，精神病學系統是一種政治逼害工具，主要用於對付蘇聯國內持不同政見人士。許多學者，包括精神科醫生，也用術語「蘇聯的政治精神病學」或「懲罰性精神病」來稱呼這個系統。<br />\n<br />\n在19世紀的俄國，有政治目的使用精神病學只是偶然的事件。這種濫用始於蘇共總書記勃列日涅夫時期，出任克格勃首長的安德羅波夫，誰公開表示不同意領導人的馬列主義官方教條，即被診斷為精神病。如參與民權行動和示威，並參與被禁止的宗教活動，也被確定為精神疾病需要被治癒。這種做法一直維持至蘇聯解體，在俄羅斯偶然也有實行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%98%87%E8%81%AF%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E7%97%85%E5%AD%B8%E7%9A%84%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E6%BF%AB%E7%94%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%2598%2587%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E7%25A5%259E%25E7%2597%2585%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E6%25BF%25AB%25E7%2594%25A8&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjNjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=1fb4ca1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%98%87%E8%81%AF%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E7%97%85%E5%AD%B8%E7%9A%84%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E6%BF%AB%E7%94%A8</a>"},{"pid":"713eb87b29e40e00aa0b3c74396c820a754a368a","tid":2061613,"uid":280648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f249e2feb53053570366bd5fc86c2d8a474f9ca9","tid":2061613,"uid":35364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T13:47:00.000Z","msg":"<strong>蘇聯精神病學的政治濫用</strong><br />\n在蘇聯，精神病學系統是一種政治逼害工具，主要用於對付蘇聯國內持不同政見人士。許多學者，包括精神科醫生，也用術語「蘇聯的政治精神病學」或「懲罰性精神病」來稱呼這個系統。<br />\n<br />\n在19世紀的俄國，有政治目的使用精神病學只是偶然的事件。這種濫用始於蘇共總書記勃列日涅夫時期，出任克格勃首長的安德羅波夫，誰公開表示不同意領導人的馬列主義官方教條，即被診斷為精神病。如參與民權行動和示威，並參與被禁止的宗教活動，也被確定為精神疾病需要被治癒。這種做法一直維持至蘇聯解體，在俄羅斯偶然也有實行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%98%87%E8%81%AF%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E7%97%85%E5%AD%B8%E7%9A%84%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E6%BF%AB%E7%94%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%2598%2587%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25B2%25BE%25E7%25A5%259E%25E7%2597%2585%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E6%25BF%25AB%25E7%2594%25A8&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjNjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=1fb4ca1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%98%87%E8%81%AF%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E7%97%85%E5%AD%B8%E7%9A%84%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E6%BF%AB%E7%94%A8</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T13:47:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />完全係極權化"},{"pid":"53c1bad2464ba20d3de19d95bbb94fdad30176c1","tid":2061613,"uid":220690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T14:02:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"07cc7fa8a4213b1b67026087452925c3e87715cb","tid":2061613,"uid":51790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T14:04:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a68c51d03d2415e47b7da6166516751c35401c4b","tid":2061613,"uid":26770,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T14:07:36.000Z","msg":"<strong>吳重儀係鋪路對付新屋嶺輪姦案受害人同x小姐</strong><br />\n呢個中學生無呢個謀算<br />\n應該係刑事檢控專員親自指揮<br />\n<br />\n鄉黑強係放棄人性的惡鬼<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但全政府我只忌梁卓然一人</span><br />\n呢個人陰險,城府好深,毫無人類底線"},{"pid":"1f11fa3e3fafdc6c52cfb08f4d8d1c40e15bed90","tid":2061613,"uid":19178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T14:10:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d02c6e8ee4175ec4ab39c9b1be0ab96c23518450","tid":2061613,"uid":54517,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T15:45:23.000Z","msg":"投訴人姓名:___________先生/小姐<br />\n<br />\n法官姓名：吳重儀<br />\n法院名稱：粉嶺裁判法院<br />\n聆訊日期：12/06/2020<br />\n案件編號：FLCC5275/2019<br />\n<br />\n本人現投訴裁判官吳重儀於審理案件(FLCC5275/2019)時嚴重偏頗警察及對被告懷有既定的負面立場，原因如下：<br />\n<br />\n1. 裁判官吳重儀於判詞中表示，案中三名警員口供不一，顯示各人沒有「夾口供」，認為三名警員誠實可靠。此說法已有問題，如該三名警員口供一致，亦可理解為三名警員同時說出事實真相，顯示警員誠實可靠，即是不論警員口供如何，裁判官吳重儀已無條件相信警員誠實可靠，由此顯示裁判官吳重儀嚴重偏頗警察。<br />\n<br />\n2. 裁判官吳重儀於判詞中表示，被告以警員編號而不是以「警察」或「差佬」稱呼，是有敵意及不尊重。此說法已有問題，警員編號是用以準確的指出警察的身份，故此警隊才會有警員編號的制度，及於警察制服上展示警員編號。目的是供大眾知悉該位警員，但裁判官吳重儀卻表示稱呼警員編號而不是「警察」，即是有敵意及不尊重，顯然裁判官吳重儀自身也對被告有既定立場。<br />\n<br />\n3. 辯方求情時指，被告受人愛戴及沒犯罪紀錄，希望以非監禁形式處理，但裁判官吳重儀表示「襲警一定判坐監」；但事實上有很多不同襲警案例皆沒有判處監禁形式處理，顯然而見，裁判官吳重儀已經無視辯方的理據，她以自己偏頗的立場審理此案件。<br />\n<br />\n綜合而言，裁判官吳重儀立場偏頗，於判詞內已明確顯示她嚴重偏頗及相信警察供詞，故本人質疑裁判官吳重儀中立的角色。<br />\n<br />\n懇請秘書處可作出合理的行動。<br />\n<br />\n投訴人簽署:<br />\n日期:12/06/2020<br />\n寄去<br />\n香港金鐘道38號<br />\n高等法院大樓<br />\n投訴法官行為秘書處"},{"pid":"968abb83302e3336a537eb655387a62eeaa62d52","tid":2061613,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T20:40:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e66a4ad1180c940c8246fd3ab1cd2f445113c34","tid":2061613,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T20:45:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"363bd7c89012e98a877e1717b186f1583683f2a7","tid":2061613,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T21:09:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"323db931a62d88cd613310a1f254d973cb35f0bf","tid":2061613,"uid":220985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T21:24:50.000Z","msg":"pish 救手足。。。"},{"pid":"1487ea05ada4289d9385469c055f91361e0e101b","tid":2061613,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T21:26:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9ee0ba53fd6796df23b1e55603ea3a01aa16b42","tid":2061613,"uid":220985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T21:40:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7c8c83f7ee8f8fa6e317eadbd377214e89c7b942","tid":2061613,"uid":220985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T21:52:10.000Z","msg":"開始推唔郁"},{"pid":"aef7e487f8ac60d6c7bd21fb56c1f7e5bf9ef750","tid":2061613,"uid":220985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T21:54:55.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"b6bec4bc576e99390cc1eee35deb7bde69328a93","tid":2061613,"uid":107368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T22:02:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef18f3383e8206a7d5e946c595dd45d2ce6c4fd5","tid":2061613,"uid":38383,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T22:05:23.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪大紀元到做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56d73ca9e23e6d5d34314bfe3c082283a7ff12de","tid":2061613,"uid":14433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T22:13:38.000Z","msg":"手足⋯⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />垃圾法官吳公義"},{"pid":"6cbffbbd8505f1b080f137d334495f0d339